Title: "Get Pokémon data for a non-existent Pokémon".

Preconditions: None (public API, no auth required)

Steps:
1. Send a GET request to: https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/pikachu123

Expected result:
1. Status code: 404
2. Response body contains: 
Not Found

## Postman Test Scripts

pm.test("Status code is 404", function () {
    pm.response.to.have.status(404);
});

pm.test("Response body says Not Found", function () {
    pm.expect(pm.response.text()).to.eql("Not Found");
});
